          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>After working with several production companies and single producers, we finally came to the conclusion that, if we want to provide steady quality and if we want to understand and know every single step of our production, we need to start producing ourselves.<br/><br/>This way we can make sure our tailors work under fair working conditions.<br/>We can make sure, that we don't use plastic.<br/>We can supervise every single step of our production and we are able to sample new products more efficiently.</p>"
